title: Kiss Man Man Medium Skin Tone Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic kiss between two men, with one having a medium skin tone and the other a light skin tone. It signifies love, affection, and same-sex relationships.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji portrays two men sharing a tender moment, rendered with Apple's signature smooth gradients and soft, rounded edges. The medium and light skin tones are depicted with subtle shading, reflecting realistic lighting that gives them a warm, inviting appearance. This representation of affection, characterized by a gentle kiss and rosy cheeks, conveys romance, partnership, and heartfelt connection within digital conversations.
